  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/c3f5bcd205d8df847bd3a222673ef5ba.avif?t=1756860539\" width=619 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing hidden object game for cat's lovers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the cats by clicking on them, in a hand-drawn background. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/77a8058c7b413fcf6554fd392911ae65.avif?t=1756860539\" width=619 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 😺200+ Cats to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨4 Locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡Hint System for cats location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😻Discover Special Cats: Upon returning to a completed level, special cats are enabled in the scenario. As an additional challenge, the hint system is not available for locating the special cats. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.poster.avif?t=1756860539\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.webm?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249850/extras/9a499095120a2d6c44cc83317a84bb24.mp4?t=1756860539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔎Zoom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌗Contrast settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵Relaxing music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨Besides the kittens, find 05 special objec